#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cache-redis-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By default, Quarkus Cache uses Caffeine as backend.\n"
"It's possible to use Redis instead."
msgstr "默认情况下，Quarkus Cache 使用 Caffeine 作为后端。也可以改用 Redis。"

